Refactor drag-and-drop functionality and cleanup WebServer nodes.
Updated the HomePage component to improve drag-and-drop usability by introducing a dedicated drag handle. Removed `SourceView` node registration from `WebServer.java` for cleanup and alignment with updated requirements.
Closed #25 dans le graph NIVO view, le popup devrait afficher le whatIsThis, la classe et le pretty_name

Refactor column logic and enhance node data handling
Refactored column count logic for better readability and maintainability in `HomePage.jsx`. Enhanced graph nodes with `prettyName`, `whatIsThis`, and `className` attributes to improve tooltip and display information. Updated layout styling and tooltip configurations for consistency and clarity.
Closed #27 show JSON as a foldable tree, everywhere

Refactor node handling and endpoint compatibility checks.
Removed unnecessary synchronization, simplified logic in `outDegree`, and updated endpoints to handle `BNode` instead of strictly `BBGraph`. Enhanced type safety and ensured backward compatibility with conditional casting.

div.div: Born into a unique world where villages fight to gain power and control, the main character, Shi Hao, is a genius blessed by the heavens born under the poorest of conditions. His clan, however, has a mysterious past. To rise up and become the genius he is meant to be, the clan goes through every effort to aid his cultivation as they battle through fanatical monsters and engage in power struggles with other clans. His journey will bring him through unknown lands until he is able to become a person that can truly shake the world.

Back then, Dok-Ja had no idea. He had no idea his favorite web novel 'Three Ways to Survive the Apocalypse' was going to come to life, and that he would become the only person to know how the world was going to end. He also had no idea he would end up becoming the protagonist of this novel-turned-reality. Now, Dok-Ja will go on a journey to change the course of the story and save humankind once and for all.
(Source: WEBTOONS, edited)

In a world where awakened beings called “Hunters” must battle deadly monsters to protect humanity, Seong Jin-U, nicknamed “the weakest hunter of all mankind,” finds himself in a constant struggle for survival. One day, after a brutal encounter in an overpowered dungeon wipes out his party and threatens to end his life, a mysterious System chooses him as its sole player: Jin-U has been granted the rare opportunity to level up his abilities, possibly beyond any known limits. Follow Jin-U’s journey as he takes on ever-stronger enemies, both human and monster, to discover the secrets deep within the dungeons and the ultimate extent of his powers. (Source: Tappytoon) Note: Chapter count includes a prologue and 21 side stories.
